name: Semi-life
body:
### Welcome to Semi-life Game Project.
in Semi-life game provides a new innovative game mechanics which simulate human real life progress ,your progress depends on two factors your decisions , your luck .

### game overView
a 3D board game ,so much similar to classic game  "snake and ladder" ,  but with new innovative ideas and featurs so it not only depends on your luck but also on your decisions .
